# macos-mcp

## Mail (write)

- Use `mail_draft_email` or `mail_draft_reply` only. Never send. User reviews in Mail.app.

## Typography (outgoing mail)

- No em dash, en dash, or spaced hyphen as punctuation in subject/body.
- Sanitizer must preserve newlines (never `\s{2,}` on full body).

## Signatures

- Set `sender`; signature from `signatures/manifest.json`.
- No `--` before signature block.

## General

- All tools are local macOS only. No cloud email APIs.
